              No clunky configs, no risky exports—just clean, safe results every
              time.
            </li>
            <li>Intuitive UI to configure data policies by user or role.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 5. Features Section -->
  <section id="features" class="py-20 bg-gray-900">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
