            You don't need sales to query a database.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-gray-400 space-y-2 list-disc pl-5">
            <li>Try it now, not after six Zoom calls.</li>
            <li>
              We're built for product-led growth—while the old guard's still
              chasing RFPs.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 4: Workflows -->
        <div
          class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-700 interactive-card glow-on-hover"
        >
          <div class="text-blue-400 mb-4">
            <svg
              class="w-12 h-12"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Workflows, To Work and Flow</h3>
